[V:8] E,/F,/ G,, G,, G,, | B,, G,, B,, | F, C, D, | E, E, E, | A,, C, F, |
%
% Bars 14-18 of B section (continuing 3/4)
%
[V:1] B3/2 A/ G | A G F | E !fermata!E E/F/ | G G G | F F F/G/ |
[V:2] G3/2 F/ E | F E D | C C C/D/ | E E E | D D D/E/ |
